
#required directory structure

genomes_and_annotations/
├── GCF_004118075.1_ASM411807v1 -> /data/norman/resources/Cowpea/GCF_004118075.1_ASM411807v1
├── readme
└── snpeffdata

# directly under genomes_and_annotations/ add directories corresponding to your genomes, they can be softlinks. The linked genome directory will need to contain the pre-processed reference genome files, ie.,

(samtools) .fa, .fai,
(bwa) .fa.amb, .fa.ann, .fa.bwt, .fa.pac, .fa.sa
(ngm) .fa-enc.2.ngm, .fa-ht-13-2.3ngm

those files need to be generated by
$ samtools faidx <reference-genome.fa>
$ bwa index -a bwtsw <reference-genome.fa>
$ ngm -r <reference-genome.fa>

(reference assemblies suffix .fna can also be used)
